    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! It\u2019s been a super reliable car for me\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. It\u2019s in solid shape, well-loved, and runs like a dream. You might find a tiny sign of use here or there, but honestly, it\u2019s a great find and totally ready to hit the road today. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
