    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s legendary S54-powered performance icon. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced VANOS system to ensure optimal cam timing. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the platform's primary structural concern. While the exterior and interior show minor wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain and drivetrain are dialed in for peak lateral acceleration and throttle response.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well.",
      "price": 31500.0,
