      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, this unit delivers a refined and reliable driving experience. Fully inspected and prepared for immediate service, it stands as a testament to balanced value and enduring performance. Inquire today to secure this exceptional example of automotive engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
