    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty\u2014it\u2019s been super reliable and still looks great on the road! It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream, perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. It's been well-loved and is totally ready for its next adventure. Drop me a message if you want to come see it or take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
