    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is complemented by a variable M-differential lock for exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, utilizing aluminum multi-link suspension and a carbon fiber roof panel to lower the center of gravity. Recent preventive maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies operate at peak efficiency. While showing minor signs of road use consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity and hydraulic steering feedback remain sharp and uncompromised.",
